extendedInfo.description: If you are Senses Fail's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Senses Fail's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Senses Fail's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Senses Fail's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)************************Main Features ************************- Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics************************List of albums ************************- From the Depths of Dreams- Let It Enfold You- Still Searching- Life Is Not a Waiting Room- The Fire- Follow Your Bliss- Renacer************************List of lyrics ************************- Ali For Cody- All The Best Cowboys Have Daddy Issues- American Death- Ancient Tombs- Angela Baker And My Obsession With Fire- Battle Hymn- Between The Mountains And The Sea- Bite To Break Skin- Blackout- Bloody Romance- Bonecrusher- Buried A Lie- Calling All Cars- Canine- Can't Be Saved- Champagne- Chandelier- Choke On This- Cinco De Mayo- Closure / Rebirth- Coming Up Short- Courage Of The Knife- Coward- DB Cooper- Dreaming A Reality- Early Graves- Every Day Is A Struggle- Family Tradition- Fireworks At Dawn- Four Years- Free Fall Without A Parachute- Frost Flower- Garden State- Ghost Town- Glass- Hair Of The Dog- Handguns And Second Chances- Headed West- Hold On- Holy Mountain- Institutionalized- Irish Eyes- Irony Of Dying On Your Birthday- Lady In A Blue Dress- Landslide- Let It Enfold You- Life Is Not A Waiting Room- Lifeboats- Lost And Found- Lungs Like Gallows- Map The Streets- Martini Kiss- Mason's Revenge- Mi Amour- Nero- New Year's Eve- NJ Falls Into The Atlantic- One Eight Seven- Renacer- Rum Is For Drinking, Not For Burning- Safe House- Saint Anthony- Salvation- Shark Attack- Sick Or Sane (Fifty For A Twenty)- Slow Dance- Snake Bite- Steven- Still Searching- Stretch Your Legs To Coffin Length- The Fire- The Ground Folds- The Ground Folds (Acoustic)- The Path- The Priest And The Matador- The Rapture- Tie Her Down- To All The Crowded Rooms- Vines- War Paint- Waves- Wolves At The Door- Yellow Angels- You're Cute When You Scream
